                                                                 "GLYPH_UI"
                                                             ],
                                      "RULES":  [
                                                    "EN FR and NATIVE_FINAL are renders, never backend sources of truth.",
                                                    "GL is the semantic truth contract.",
                                                    "GL_G compresses canonical semantics, not raw prose.",
                                                    "GLYPH_UI is illustrative and must not be required for backend execution.",
                                                    "GPV2 backend must preserve uncertainty, risk and constraints."
