                                                           "BACKEND_ROUTING_DECISIONS"
                                                       ],
                                      "RULES":  [
                                                    "No sensitive FACT enters backend stable flow without HGOV pass.",
                                                    "No cache write as stable when risk status is CRITICAL unresolved.",
                                                    "GL_G must preserve risk or uncertainty state needed by routing.",
                                                    "Memory promotion requires HGOV clean status or explicit downgrade."
                                                ]
                                  },
